[explanation]The management console is sometimes referred to as Tahoe, but actually Tahoe is the full system - the LMS, Studio, Figures, and the management console. Tahoe isn't something that can just be added to another Open edX site! Only Appsembler customers have access to Tahoe and its management console, as it was developed here and we have yet to take it into the world of open source.[explanation]
